metadata.name: Liam
metadata.description:
LOM BABY is a new life form.
Our goal is to meld with humanity and to meld the world of LOM into an existence equal to that of the real world.
Therefore, they may act and behave in a very cute way, imitating the wisdom of the human race, but please love them with all your heart.
Please love them honestly, and they will become very important to you someday.
